high_descs: Turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife to the left of the sink.
Rinse off the knife in the sink and pick it back up.
Go right to the coffee maker.
Put the knife on the counter in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed knife on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the right, turn left, then turn right again and walk to the sink
Pick up the knife from the sink
Place the knife in the sink, rinse with water, pick the knife back up
Turn to the right, walk to the coffee maker
Place the knife in front of the coffee maker
Go forward and turn to the right to face the sink.
Pick the knife up from the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the knife up again.
Move to the right and face the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the knife down on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife on the counter.
